{"tid":118052,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［咪比錢中介］係兄弟做左7年，你問我答？","createTime":"2017-02-12T17:06:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-07T04:20:15.000Z","uid":77256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c51d1ccd7e3df27fd535c8a83d662b8432eda317","tid":118052,"uid":77256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T17:06:13.000Z","msg":"請出招， 唔會自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n答到都會答， 即管問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"176d334cecb31cf70586b1a3ced1dad6ca28e983","tid":118052,"uid":77256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T17:10:09.000Z","msg":"連登仔 個個都借到熟晒 唔洗問？"},{"pid":"36efee79e7701145682e064327d5ff7a745c0565","tid":118052,"uid":26389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T17:12:46.000Z","msg":"借錢唔還會點 比黑社會處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da5d7edacb5168087058046e6786d7fe52bd57e6","tid":118052,"uid":77256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T17:15:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>借錢唔還會點 比黑社會處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係收唔到數 就會賣條數 比d收數公司， 之後就唔關我地事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffbeb8542d71bb231eb8a5b6a010164e317c7fa9","tid":118052,"uid":55830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T17:23:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>借錢唔還會點 比黑社會處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係收唔到數 就會賣條數 比d收數公司， 之後就唔關我地事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收數公司會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e59ab5dd269a6c26e6c6f2ecb881edbe5c014ee","tid":118052,"uid":26389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T17:26:31.000Z","msg":"搵中介既目的是咪避免整花自己個信貸紀錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1facde83c2b1a88d1ecb97bf9866bfddb4d10ae4","tid":118052,"uid":77256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T22:46:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>借錢唔還會點 比黑社會處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係收唔到數 就會賣條數 比d收數公司， 之後就唔關我地事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收數公司會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打電話比你全家煩下你地， 係你門口貼下大字報，無咩可以做。  佢攪你 報警就得， 佢實笠水 放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔理佢既話 玩一排佢就放棄。"},{"pid":"cd71bde7f9ddf53e906d5393a6025b1e8ddeb215","tid":118052,"uid":77256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T22:50:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵中介既目的是咪避免整花自己個信貸紀錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正常你借錢準還個底都唔借花， 除非你本身花左借唔到先要去中介借， 咁介洗咩理花唔花。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a718f10e89a30ee5bb1e26f99ce7bed8ae72b1a","tid":118052,"uid":77256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T23:06:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搵中介既目的是咪避免整花自己個信貸紀錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正常你借錢準<span style=\"color: red;\">時</span>還個底都唔<span style=\"color: red;\">會</span>花， 除非你本身花左借唔到先要去中介借， 咁<span style=\"color: red;\">仲</span>洗咩理花唔花。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"7933da65d9ca8377cd42a51df845e39b2dc9eacc","tid":118052,"uid":112583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T03:12:05.000Z","msg":"樓主仲係唔係度?<br />\n<br />\n破左產係咪仲可以keep住借財仔?"},{"pid":"878ac06b3e44a7b1b40439a79ad25c5b776a0ed3","tid":118052,"uid":77256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T03:36